00:40:10,560 --> 00:40:12,720
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, sorry, to nisam predao svoje srce.

391
00:40:13,120 --> 00:40:14,800
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ono, predajem u svoje srce.

392
00:40:15,520 --> 00:40:15,600
